import { Typography, Grid, Box } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Comment = (props) => {
  return (
    <Grid container spacing={2} paddingTop={2} paddingRight={2}>
    <Grid item xs={8} md={8}>
       <Typography variant="subtitle2" sx={{color : "white"}}>{props.username}</Typography>
    </Grid>
    <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
        <Box p={2} sx= {{ backgroundColor : "#226597" , borderRadius : "5px"}}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{color : "white"}} >InfoBot Q&A</Typography>
            <hr/>
        </Box>
    </Grid>
</Grid>
  )
}

export default Comment;
